pageType: content
background:
  type: image
  src: https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85f82e?w=1920&q=80
  fit:
    mode: cover
  mask:
    type: gradient
    gradientType: linear
    angle: 0
    stops:
      - position: 0
        color: "#2A242080"
      - position: 0.4
        color: "#2A2420B0"
      - position: 1
        color: "#2A2420E0"
elements:
  - elementId: quote-en
    elementType: text
    bounds:
      - 80
      - 160
      - 700
      - 50
    wrap: false
    content:
      fontSize: 22
      color: "#FFFFFFAA"
      fontFamily: Oranienbaum, siyuanSongti
      wrap: false
      align:
        - left
        - middle
      text: |
        <p><em>Innocence is a daring adventure.</em></p>
  - elementId: quote-cn
    elementType: text
    bounds:
      - 80
      - 220
      - 700
      - 80
    wrap: false
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: $white
      fontFamily: Oranienbaum, siyuanSongti
      wrap: false
      align:
        - left
        - middle
      text: |
        <p><strong>天真是一种冒险。</strong></p>
  - elementId: narrative
    elementType: text
    bounds:
      - 80
      - 340
      - 550
      - 180
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF99"
      fontFamily: Liter, MiSans
      lineHeight: 2
      align:
        - left
        - top
      text: |
        <p>MM captures the essence of a daring spirit. Where others seek conformity, MM embraces the radical innocence of youth — its awkwardness, its beauty, its power. Fashion is not mere adornment; it is a declaration of selfhood, a rebellion whispered through pleats and prints, buttons and bows.</p>
  - elementId: logo-bottom
    elementType: text
    bounds:
      - 900
      - 580
      - 300
      - 60
    wrap: false
    content:
      fontSize: 44
      color: $white
      fontFamily: Oranienbaum, siyuanSongti
      letterSpacing: 10
      wrap: false
      align:
        - right
        - middle
      text: |
        <p><strong>FASHION</strong></p>
